  "body": "# Altair(HF1) Official Tracking\r\n\r\n# Detailed tracking\r\n## ⭐ Beacon Chain\r\n### New objects in Altair format\r\n#### Protobuf definitions EthereumAPI\r\n- [x] Beacon block Altair https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/ethereumapis/pull/234\r\n- [x] Beacon state Altair #8581 #8641 \r\n- [x] Sync aggregate https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/ethereumapis/pull/234\r\n- [x] Sync committee #8581 #8641\r\n- [x] Validator sync committee signature containers\r\n   - [x] `SyncCommitteeSigningData` in types.proto #8870\r\n   - [x] Rest is in ethereumAPI  https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/ethereumapis/pull/237\r\n\r\n#### Protobuf definitions Eth2API\r\n- [x] Beacon block Altair https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/ethereumapis/pull/230\r\n- [x] Beacon state Altair\r\n- [x] Sync aggregate\r\n- [x] Sync committee\r\n\r\n#### Custom type\r\n- [x] Go-bitfield: Bitvector[SYNC_COMMITTEE_SIZE] https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/go-bitfield/pull/33\r\n- [ ] Eth2-type: ParticipationFlags\r\n\r\n### Altair configs\r\n- [x] Mainnet #8642 \r\n- [x] Minimal #8642 \r\n\r\n### New beacon state pkg for Altair\r\n- [x] Revamp beacon state phase0 pkg in anticipation of Altair #8533 #8544 #8552 #8589 #8609 #8615 #8620 #8630 #8633 #8650 #8705 #8704 #8698 #8696 #8653 #8767 #8773 #8781\r\n- [x] Implement beacon state Altair pkg #8670 #8658 #8673 #8690 #8856\r\n- [x] Test utility setup to initialize beacon state Altair #8716 \r\n\r\n### Core processing pkgs\r\n- [x] Genesis state init for interop and testing #8712 #8713  \r\n- [x] Sync committees to support light clients #8717 #8721 #8728\r\n- [x] New accounting reform #8461 #8729 #8731  #8753\r\n- [x] New slashing parameters #8732\r\n- [x] Per validator inactivity leak  #8753 #8762\r\n- [x] New process block #8784\r\n- [x] New process epoch #8772 #8797 #8841 #8857\r\n- [x] New state transition #8796\r\n\r\n### DB pkg\r\n- [x] Signed beacon block Altair\r\n- [x] Beacon state Altair\r\n- [x] Handling Different Data Types For Phase 0/Altair Objects.\r\n\r\n### Cache pkg\r\n- [x] Sync committee indices cache #8884\r\n- [x] Beacon state Altair\r\n\r\n### Networking\r\n- [x] Gossip Validation Addition\r\n- [x] Beacon block gossip topic for new Altair type\r\n- [x] Gossip For Sync Committee Aggregates\r\n- [x ] Gossip Subnets for Sync Committee Contribution\r\n- [x] Processing Path for Sync Committee Aggregate\r\n- [x] Processing Path for Sync Committee Contribution\r\n- [x] Refactoring RPC handles to take in context\r\n- [x] Add in v2 Path for Req/Resp Topics. \r\n- [x] Fork Awareness Logic For Gossip/RPC(Req/Resp).\r\n- [x] Registering For Sync Committee Subnets.\r\n- [x] Adjusting Discovery For Different Forks.\r\n\r\n### RPC\r\n- [x] Validator sync committee assignments\r\n- [x] Sync committee aggregates in beacon blocks\r\n- [x] Block proposal for Altair\r\n\r\n### Fork logic\r\n- [x] Switch over Phase 0 beacon state to an Altair beacon state\r\n\r\n### Weak subjectivity\r\n- [x] New weak subjectivity period calculations and sample values\r\n\r\n## ⭐ Validator\r\n- [x] Helpers for RPC server in https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/dev/specs/altair/validator.md\r\n- [x] Service definitions on ethereumapi\r\n- [x] Proposer to package new beacon block body with sync aggregate\r\n- [x] Attester to submit sync committee signature\r\n- [x] Aggregator to aggregate sync committee signatures\r\n- [x] Validator client must have fork awareness, we need design\r\n\r\n## ⭐ Testing\r\n- [x] Phase 0 spec tests clean up #8798 #8800 #8826\r\n- [x] Altair spec tests\r\n    - [x] Operations #8795\r\n    - [x] Epoch #8806\r\n    - [x] Rewards #8818 \r\n    - [x] Sanity #8831\r\n    - [x] SSZ static #8847\r\n- [x] Duplicate e2e tests to cover hard fork code paths\r\n- [x] E2E tests to cover the switch over in various hard fork combinations \r\n\r\n## ⭐ Misc\r\n- [x] Merge our custom changes to fastssz into upstream to avoid using forks of the repo in go.mod",
